<p>As a crypto beginner, you might be wondering if it&#8217;s worth it to buy just one bitcoin. Well, the answer depends on your financial goals and investment strategy. If you&#8217;re looking to hold Bitcoin long-term, buying one bitcoin can give you exposure to the crypto market without having to invest a significant amount of capital.</p>



